    "date": "2019-07-01T13:14:41Z",
    "text": "Tax Equity Act of 2019\n\nThis bill provides for regional cost-of-living adjustments in individual income tax rates. The bill also directs the Department of Labor to determine and publish a cost-of-living index for each statistical area for 2019 and each calendar year thereafter. A \"statistical area\" is (1) any metropolitan statistical area as defined by the Department of Commerce, and (2) the portion of any state not within a metropolitan statistical area."
